title: Rampant false bans
text:
This app has a major issue with falsely banning people, especially without warning. You‚Äôll log on one day without violating any rules and find your account banned, and appeals take time IF (and that‚Äôs a very big if) they even go through. Customer support is also nonexistent, it‚Äôs nearly all automated and talking with another person to resolve false-bans, reset a phone number, deal with hacking problems, or solve any other issues is impossible.
I was depending on this app to talk with people overseas and now cannot communicate with any international friends, colleagues, or family.
If you rely on this app for work or communication, stop. Make sure to always have a backup method of communication because you may find yourself unable to use this app one day for no reason, wether that be for 24  hours in the best case or permanently at worst. If you can‚Äôt afford this risk of random bans then just avoid the app.
